Class CodeRefactorabilitySettings

java.lang.Object
ac.code.verifier.configuration.CodeRefactorabilitySettings
public class CodeRefactorabilitySettings extends Object
The class CodeRefactorabilitySettings stores the settings of ExtractableCode annotation.
